# Foundry Identity

MasterClass teaches ("Watch this."). Foundry transforms ("Become this.").

## Every User Has

- Mastery titles (Bourbon Steward, Pitmaster, etc.)
- Active paths with progress %
- Collections, reviews, paths completed, communities led
- One identity across web verticals + single Foundry mobile app

## Package

`@foundry/ownership-graph` — `buildFoundryIdentity()`, `EXAMPLE_STEVE_IDENTITY`

## Viral Loop

Share **what I'm becoming** — not what I consumed.

## Device Strategy

- Web: vertical domains (bourbon.foundryos.com)
- Mobile: **one Foundry app** — NOT per-vertical apps
- Auth: Google, Apple, Email, Magic Link (Supabase)

